{"type":"queue-operation","operation":"enqueue","timestamp":"2026-05-02T01:16:41.280Z","sessionId":"55811d4e-34d6-42df-9582-284664a6a576","content":"<task-notification>\n<task-id>a7e0c365f90bdef62</task-id>\n<tool-use-id>REDACTED</tool-use-id>\n<output-file>/private/tmp/claude-501/-Users-dcambria-scripts-server-tools-v2-docker-dev-sites-concertacao/7507f46e-7685-4d92-859f-ad4eecb68375/tasks/a7e0c365f90bdef62.output</output-file>\n<status>completed</status>\n<summary>Agent \"Ciclo C — mu-plugin tunnel host fix\" completed</summary>\n<result>Validação final OK. Reporte:\n\n---\n\n**CICLO C — Concluído**\n\n**Diff aplicado em `bit_elc_make_relative()`:**\n\nRemovida a comparação `$site_host !== $url_host` (que falhava no cenário tunnel onde `home_url()` retorna `cambrasmax.local` mas `tunnel-url-rewrite.php` ja reescreveu para `concertacao.bureau-it.com`). Substituída por path-heuristic:\n\n```php\n$path = parse_url( $url, PHP_URL_PATH );\nif ( ! is_string( $path ) || $path === '' ) {\n    return $url;\n}\nif ( strpos( $path, '/wp-content/uploads/' ) === false ) {\n    return $url;\n}\n$qs = parse_url( $url, PHP_URL_QUERY );\nreturn $path . ( $qs ? '?' . $qs : '' );\n```\n\nMantém URLs externas genuínas (S3, CDN) intactas — elas não terão `/wp-content/uploads/` no path. Comentário da seção (4) atualizado explicando o motivo da troca.\n\n**Validação E2E:**\n- CSS pós-tunnel-warm (`https://concertacao.bureau-it.com/`): `url(\"/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/...jpg\")` — **path-relative confirmado**\n- CSS pós-local-warm (`https://cambrasmax.local:8484/`): mesma URL — **path-relative preservado**\n- Cross-warm (local primeiro, tunnel depois): mesma URL — **path-relative estável**\n\n**Versionamento:**\n- `2.1.0` → `2.1.1` (header + comentário seção 4) — fix do bug tunnel host\n- Em paralelo, terceiro ajuste bumpou para `2.1.2` (perf optimization no debug_backtrace caching) — preservado, fix v2.1.1 mantido intacto na função\n\n**Sincronia espelho:**\n- Canônico: `/Users/dcambria/scripts/server-tools/v2/docker-dev/common/mu-plugins/bit-elementor-local-cache.php`\n- Espelho: `/Users/dcambria/scripts/server-tools/v2/docker-dev/sites/concertacao/wordpress/wp-content/mu-plugins/bit-elementor-local-cache.php`\n- `diff -q` retorna idêntico, ambos em v2.1.2\n\n**Não deployado em prod** (prod continua v2.0.2). **Não commitado** (apenas editado conforme instrução).</result>\n<usage><total_tokens>67930</total_tokens><tool_uses>23</tool_uses><duration_ms>202150</duration_ms></usage>\n</task-notification>"}
{"parentUuid":"fbae9f8e-016e-45ea-825c-b71ee34b32bb","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-7","id":"msg_01Jtrr2Bva5JQNjfERxEHeCh","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Ciclo B+ revelou **mais 1 script bugado** (`phase4-create-test-rule.sh`). Sobre `/conhecimento/` (post-2.css):\n\n**Achado crítico:** prod tem **DOIS paths** com `post-2.css`:\n- `/var/www/.../uploads/s3/concertacaoamazonia.com.br/assets/uploads/elementor/css/post-2.css` (path antigo S3-Uploads)\n- `/var/www/.../wp-content/elementor-cache/elementor/css/post-2.css` (path novo do mu-plugin)\n\nApós `flush_css`, o `/elementor-cache/` foi apagado. **`HTTP=404` no warm-up** indica que `/conhecimento/` retorna 404 internamente (mas ele responde 200 publicamente — é o nginx proxy 8080 só responder em `/health`). Vou pre-warm correto:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":3629,"cache_read_input_tokens":613496,"output_tokens":810,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":3629,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[{"input_tokens":1,"output_tokens":810,"cache_read_input_tokens":613496,"cache_creation_input_tokens":3629,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":3629},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"diagnostics":null},"requestId":"req_011CacrmxS5iaPvqdNueEF8X","type":"assistant","uuid":"9337a274-f37a-4515-8c3b-17af940dc3f3","timestamp":"2026-05-02T01:16:47.301Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/dcambria/scripts/server-tools/v2/docker-dev/sites/concertacao","sessionId":"55811d4e-34d6-42df-9582-284664a6a576","version":"2.1.126","gitBranch":"main","slug":"prepare-o-deploy-do-snappy-taco"}
{"parentUuid":"9337a274-f37a-4515-8c3b-17af940dc3f3","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-7","id":"msg_01Jtrr2Bva5JQNjfERxEHeCh","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_017Lue3hSPEh2xKdBjW1BFoi","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"echo \"=== Pre-warm /conhecimento/ pelo proxy correto (porta 80, host header) ===\"\nssh concertacaoamazonia.com.br-prod-sa \"\nsudo curl -sk -o /dev/null -w 'HTTP=%{http_code}\\\\n' \\\n  --resolve concertacaoamazonia.com.br:443:127.0.0.1 \\\n  https://concertacaoamazonia.com.br/conhecimento/\n\"\n\n# fallback alternativo\nssh concertacaoamazonia.com.br-prod-sa \"\nsudo curl -sko /dev/null -w 'HTTP=%{http_code} time=%{time_total}\\\\n' \\\n  -H 'Host: concertacaoamazonia.com.br' \\\n  -H 'X-Forwarded-Proto: https' \\\n  http://127.0.0.1/conhecimento/\n\"\n\nsleep 1\necho \"\"\necho \"=== Foi gerado agora? ===\"\nssh concertacaoamazonia.com.br-prod-sa \"sudo ls -la /var/www/concertacaoamazonia.com.br/wp-content/elementor-cache/elementor/css/post-2.css 2>&1 | head -2\"","description":"Try alternate prewarm"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":3629,"cache_read_input_tokens":613496,"output_tokens":810,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":3629,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[{"input_tokens":1,"output_tokens":810,"cache_read_input_tokens":613496,"cache_creation_input_tokens":3629,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":3629},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"diagnostics":null},"requestId":"req_011CacrmxS5iaPvqdNueEF8X","type":"assistant","uuid":"202ef28c-e96c-4e6f-b17a-02f41ca77441","timestamp":"2026-05-02T01:16:52.184Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/dcambria/scripts/server-tools/v