{"parentUuid":"863b747e-921c-4f4e-bcd1-68b9b544a962","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-7","id":"msg_01SE6tSQGf99RezykxqaAR89","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01SWeMyr28ufDK66NXz94zU8","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"cd /Users/dcambria/scripts/server-tools/v2/docker-dev/sites/concertacao\ngit add .claude/commands/smoke.md\ngit commit -m \"$(cat <<'EOF'\nfeat(smoke): captura console_errors + failed_resources na Fase 7.5\n\nAuditoria de paths agora detecta regressoes JS/asset que nao apareciam\nna altura/headings/sections. Smoke completo em prod (2026-05-02) validou:\n\nAdicoes:\n- page.on('console') captura msg.type() === 'error'\n- page.on('response') captura 4xx/5xx em assets do proprio dominio\n  (filtra externos: CDN, ads, analytics)\n- Cleanup dos handlers em finally{} (evita memory leak entre paths)\n- Novos campos no objeto de retorno: console_errors[], console_error_count,\n  failed_resources[], failed_resource_count\n\nNovos gates (Fase 7.5 / Gate 13):\n- prod_console_errors.length > 0 → FAIL (TypeError, MIME refused, CORS)\n- prod_failed_resources.length > 0 → FAIL (assets quebrados)\n- dev > prod → WARN nao-bloqueante\n\nFalsos positivos documentados (NAO falham gate):\n- JQMIGRATE warnings (info, nao tipo error)\n- SES Removing unpermitted intrinsics (MetaMask lockdown)\n- YouTube web-share / postMessage warnings\n- YouTube iframe_api blocked pre-cookie-consent (CSP correto)\n\nBumps de threshold (descoberto em smoke real):\n- height_diff_pct: 15 -> 20 (absorve banner Complianz residual)\n- images_diff_pct: 30 -> 40 (lazy-load assincrono varia naturalmente)\n\nValidacao: smoke completo em prod retornou 16/17 PASS + 1 falso positivo\n(/agenda-geral/ Δimg=62%, confirmado com auto-scroll que ambos tem 13 imgs).\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 <noreply@anthropic.com>\nEOF\n)\"\n\necho \"\"\ngit push origin main 2>&1 | tail -3","description":"Commit and push smoke v3"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":292,"cache_read_input_tokens":792619,"output_tokens":848,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":292,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[{"input_tokens":1,"output_tokens":848,"cache_read_input_tokens":792619,"cache_creation_input_tokens":292,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":292},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"diagnostics":null},"requestId":"req_011CacvTDUPbst37Gqrq24tm","type":"assistant","uuid":"0e60f554-f6c1-4aff-abfb-69a6eec19d89","timestamp":"2026-05-02T02:05:08.127Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/dcambria/scripts/server-tools/v2/docker-dev/sites/concertacao","sessionId":"55811d4e-34d6-42df-9582-284664a6a576","version":"2.1.126","gitBranch":"main","slug":"prepare-o-deploy-do-snappy-taco"}
