://concertacao-manutencao para o bucket ativo, padronizar nomes como error-{CODE}.html, atualizar CF, deletar bucket legado","activeForm":"Promovendo versão superior e padronizando páginas de erro","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"30","subject":"Re-import banco green com dump fresco do DEV","description":"Banco green parou em 24/04 — DEV tem edits de 28/04. Export fresco DEV → S3 green/sql → import script 09 + cache flush + warm-up","activeForm":"Re-importando banco green a partir de dump fresco do DEV","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"31","subject":"Sync wp-content DEV → S3 → green (paridade total)","description":"Export wp-content do DEV, subir pra S3 path green, rodar script 10 na green para paridade total","activeForm":"Sincronizando wp-content DEV → S3 → green","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"32","subject":"Sync DEV → S3 prd-sa/green/uploads → green EC2 (incremental)","description":"Sync delta DEV→S3, depois S3→EC2 green via aws s3 sync (140 arquivos novos)","activeForm":"Sincronizando DEV → S3 → green via incremental","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"33","subject":"Opção 1: Aumentar EBS green 30GB → 60GB + sync uploads","description":"modify-volume + growpart + resize2fs + aws s3 sync S3 → EC2 para paridade total local","activeForm":"Expandindo EBS e sincronizando uploads para EC2","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"34","subject":"Opção 2: Ativar S3-Uploads na green (servir via S3, filesystem fallback)","description":"Plugin S3-Uploads + define S3_UPLOADS_BUCKET + reload FPM + smoke test (filesystem mantido como backup)","activeForm":"Ativando S3-Uploads na green","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"35","subject":"Migração C: CloudFront-OAC servindo /uploads/* do S3 (green/blue)","description":"3 ciclos × 5 agentes — análise, implementação, validação. Critério: 0 imagens 404, paridade visual blue↔green, rollback time<5min","activeForm":"Migrando para serving via CloudFront-OAC","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"36","subject":"Ciclo 3 ajustado: apply apenas green (canary, sem swap behavior principal)","description":"Publish CF Function + criar policies/origins + behavior canary específico para X-Test-Green. Blue intocado.","activeForm":"Aplicando CF-OAC apenas na green via canary path","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"37","subject":"B+C: canary multisite + validação E2E paridade visual","description":"Adicionar 2º behavior cobrindo /*/wp-content/uploads/_oac-canary/* + Playwright em 20 endpoints do A4","activeForm":"Adicionando canary multisite + validando E2E paridade visual","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"38","subject":"Ciclo 4: cutover real CF-OAC zero downtime","description":"Sync green→assets + swap behavior wp-content/uploads/* ALB→S3-uploads-prod + validate + ativar S3-Uploads no blue","activeForm":"Executando cutover real CF-OAC zero downtime","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"39","subject":"Re-import DB dev→green para corrigir WPML Atlas EN","description":"Export fresh dev DB → S3 green/sql → script 09 import → cleanup + flush. Setting WPML do dev tem display-as-translated correto.","activeForm":"Re-importando DB dev→green para corrigir Atlas EN","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"40","subject":"Documentar fix: Origin Request Policy default → Managed-AllViewer","description":"DefaultCacheBehavior OriginRequestPolicy mudada de WP-Dynamic-ForwardHostQS para Managed-AllViewer pra X-Test-Green chegar ao ALB","activeForm":"Documentando fix Origin Request Policy","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"41","subject":"Testar PDFs/jet_download em green","description":"Validar que PDFs e downloads via JetEngine funcionam na green com X-Test-Green","activeForm":"Testando PDFs/jet_download em green","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"42","subject":"Testar filtros da espiral em green","description":"Validar que cliques na espiral ativam filtros JetEngine em /conhecimento/espiral-de-conhecimento/","activeForm":"Testando filtros da espiral em green","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"43","subject":"Export DB dev + upload S3 dev/sql","description":"Rodar std export-db no dev (gera dump e sobe para s3://concertacao-backups/concertacao/dev/sql/)","activeForm":"Exportando DB do dev","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"44","subject":"Export wp-content dev + upload S3","description":"Rodar std export-wpcontent --include-uploads (sync incremental de mu-plugins, themes, plugins, uploads)","activeForm":"Exportando wp-content do dev","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"45","subject":"Copiar dev→green no S3","description":"aws s3 cp dos arquivos de dev/sql e dev/wp para green/sql e green/wp","activeForm":"Copiando arquivos dev→green no S3","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"46","subject":"Import DB na green via 09-importdatabase.sh","description":"SSH green-sa rodar 09-importdatabase.sh (drop+recreate DB, search-replace, ATE WPML cleanup, FQDN swap)","activeForm":"Importando DB na green","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"47","subject":"Import wp-content na green","description":"SSH green-sa rodar 10-importwpcontent.sh (themes/plugins/mu-plugins) + sync de uploads se necessario","activeForm":"Importando wp-content na green","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"48","subject":"Validar green pos-sync (smoke + jet_download + espiral)","description":"curl + comparacoes blue/green: home, atlas, jet_download, filtros JSF, salts (devem estar iguais ao blue)","activeForm":"Validando green pos-sync","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"49","subject":"Comparar dev vs green: páginas do menu","description":"Comparar visualmente/por content cada página: home, atlas, espiral, demais. Reportar diferenças e propor fix.","activeForm":"Comparando dev vs green pagina por pagina","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"50","subject":"Limpar S3 green de Elementor CSS vazado","description":"aws s3 rm dos post-XX.css em green/uploads/elementor/ e green/uploads/sites/2/elementor/ para garantir comportamento determinístico","activeForm":"Limpando S3 green de Elementor CSS vazado","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"51","subject":"Mu-plugin v2.0.0 com pre-warmup do static cache","description":"Reescrever bit-elementor-local-cache.php para pre-aquecer Base::$wp_uploads_dir com path local antes do S3-Uploads","activeForm":"Reescrevendo bit-elementor-local-cache v2.0.0","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"52","subject":"Deploy mu-plugin v2 na green + flush + regenerar","description":"Rsync mu-plugin novo para green, apagar elementor-cache antigo, wp elementor flush_css, validar URLs no HTML","activeForm":"Deployando mu-plugin v2 na green","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"53","subject":"CF behaviors */elementor/css/* → ALB (defesa em profundidade)","description":"Adicionar 4 behaviors CloudFront para capturar URLs legadas de elementor CSS em filesystem path → ALB","activeForm":"Adicionando CF behaviors elementor/css → ALB","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"54","subject":"Fix CF cache pollution + keepalive","description":"Auditoria 10 agentes — aplicar 3 fixes CF + Playwright + invalidate","activeForm":"Aplicando fixes CF","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]}],"itemCount":32},"type":"attachment","uuid":"92fd59e0-d884-4a81-af86-e01cdfe0b61e","timestamp":"2026-05-02T02:12:51.774Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/dcambria/scripts/server-tools/v2/docker-dev/sites/concertacao","sessionId":"55811d4e-34d6-42df-9582-284664a6a576","version":"2.1.126","gitBranch":"main","slug":"prepare-o-deploy-do-snappy-taco"}
