veForm":"Migrando para serving via CloudFront-OAC","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"36","subject":"Ciclo 3 ajustado: apply apenas green (canary, sem swap behavior principal)","description":"Publish CF Function + criar policies/origins + behavior canary específico para X-Test-Green. Blue intocado.","activeForm":"Aplicando CF-OAC apenas na green via canary path","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"37","subject":"B+C: canary multisite + validação E2E paridade visual","description":"Adicionar 2º behavior cobrindo /*/wp-content/uploads/_oac-canary/* + Playwright em 20 endpoints do A4","activeForm":"Adicionando canary multisite + validando E2E paridade visual","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"38","subject":"Ciclo 4: cutover real CF-OAC zero downtime","description":"Sync green→assets + swap behavior wp-content/uploads/* ALB→S3-uploads-prod + validate + ativar S3-Uploads no blue","activeForm":"Executando cutover real CF-OAC zero downtime","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"39","subject":"Re-import DB dev→green para corrigir WPML Atlas EN","description":"Export fresh dev DB → S3 green/sql → script 09 import → cleanup + flush. Setting WPML do dev tem display-as-translated correto.","activeForm":"Re-importando DB dev→green para corrigir Atlas EN","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"40","subject":"Documentar fix: Origin Request Policy default → Managed-AllViewer","description":"DefaultCacheBehavior OriginRequestPolicy mudada de WP-Dynamic-ForwardHostQS para Managed-AllViewer pra X-Test-Green chegar ao ALB","activeForm":"Documentando fix Origin Request Policy","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"41","subject":"Testar PDFs/jet_download em green","description":"Validar que PDFs e downloads via JetEngine funcionam na green com X-Test-Green","activeForm":"Testando PDFs/jet_download em green","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"42","subjec