erenças e propor fix.","activeForm":"Comparando dev vs green pagina por pagina","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"50","subject":"Limpar S3 green de Elementor CSS vazado","description":"aws s3 rm dos post-XX.css em green/uploads/elementor/ e green/uploads/sites/2/elementor/ para garantir comportamento determinístico","activeForm":"Limpando S3 green de Elementor CSS vazado","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"51","subject":"Mu-plugin v2.0.0 com pre-warmup do static cache","description":"Reescrever bit-elementor-local-cache.php para pre-aquecer Base::$wp_uploads_dir com path local antes do S3-Uploads","activeForm":"Reescrevendo bit-elementor-local-cache v2.0.0","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"52","subject":"Deploy mu-plugin v2 na green + flush + regenerar","description":"Rsync mu-plugin novo para green, apagar elementor-cache antigo, wp elementor flush_css, validar URLs no HTML","activeForm":"Deployando mu-plugin v2 na green","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"53","subject":"CF behaviors */elementor/css/* → ALB (defesa em profundidade)","description":"Adicionar 4 behaviors CloudFront para capturar URLs legadas de elementor CSS em filesystem path → ALB","activeForm":"Adicionando CF behaviors elementor/css → ALB","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"54","subject":"Fix CF cache pollution + keepalive","description":"Auditoria 10 agentes — aplicar 3 fixes CF + Playwright + invalidate","activeForm":"Aplicando fixes CF","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]}],"itemCount":32},"type":"attachment","uuid":"5054ada1-ce24-4108-b0ca-855ed48ae8c1","timestamp":"2026-05-02T02:53:07.684Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/dcambria/scripts/server-tools/v2/docker-dev/sites/concertacao","sessionId":"55811d4e-34d6-42df-9582-284664a6a576","version":"2.1.126","gitBranch":"main","slug":"prepare-o-deploy-do-snappy-taco"}
{"parentUuid":"5054ada1-ce24-4108-b0ca-855ed48ae8c1","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-7","id":"msg_01Xteu4D8F88rruZuWu9EmCK","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"27 options faltando. Vou copiar todas do blog 1 → blog 2 (com cuidado pra excluir options de tracking interno que devem ser por blog):"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2319,"cache_read_input_tokens":901531,"output_tokens":1445,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":2319,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[{"input_tokens":1,"output_tokens":1445,"cache_read_input_tokens":901531,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2319,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":2319},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"diagnostics":null},"requestId":"req_011Cacz8mcrE12Sh1g6BuELv","type":"assistant","uuid":"d14d669e-4e1c-40d5-b962-19653efdacb5","timestamp":"2026-05-02T02:53:13.940Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/dcambria/scripts/server-tools/v2/docker-dev/sites/concertacao","sessionId":"55811d4e-34d6-42df-9582-284664a6a576","version":"2.1.126","gitBranch":"main","slug":"prepare-o-deploy-do-snappy-taco"}
{"parentUuid":"d14d669e-4e1c-40d5-b962-19653efdacb5","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-7","id":"msg_01Xteu4D8F88rruZuWu9EmCK","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01777mKD2Pw9ZhiCXkdjGzj8","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"DEV_WP=\"/Users/dcambria/scripts/server-tools/v2/docker-dev/common/bin/docker-dev.sh\"\n\necho \"=== Copiar 27 options faltantes do blog 1 → blog 2 ===\"\n$DEV_WP wp --url=\"https://cambrasmax.local:8484/cultura\" eval '\nglobal $wpdb;\n$blog1 = $wpdb->get_col(\"SELECT option_name FROM wp_options WHERE option_name LIKE \\\"cmplz%\\\" OR option_name LIKE \\\"complianz%\\\"\");\n$blog2 = $wpdb->get_col(\"SELECT option_name FROM wp_2_options WHERE option_name LIKE \\\"cmplz%\\\" OR option_name LIKE \\\"complianz%\\\"\");\n$missing = array_diff($blog1, $blog2);\n\n// Excluir options que devem ser por-blog (tracking de scan, ativação, etc)\n$skip = [\n    \"cmplz_activation_time\",          // timestamp de ativacao do plugin no blog\n    \"cmplz_first_sync_started\",       // tracking interno por blog\n    \"cmplz_last_cookie_sync\",         // tracking interno por blog\n    \"cmplz_wsc_checks_scan_createdAt\", \"cmplz_wsc_checks_scan_id\",\n    \"cmplz_wsc_newsletter_dismissed\", \"cmplz_wsc_onboarding_dismissed\",\n    \"cmplz_wsc_signup_status\", \"cmplz_wsc_websitescan_dismissed\",\n    \"cmplz_sync_cookies_after_services_complete\", \"cmplz_sync_cookies_complete\",\n    \"cmplz_sync_services_complete\", \"cmplz_cookie_data_verified_date\",\n];\n\n$copied = 0;\n$skipped_count = 0;\nforeach ($missing as $opt_name) {\n    if (in_array($opt_name, $skip, true)) { $skipped_count++; continue; }\n    $value = get_blog_option(1, $opt_name);\n    if ($value !== false) {\n        update_option($opt_name, $value, true);\n        $copied++;\n    }\n}\n\necho \"Total faltantes: \" . count($missing) . \"\\n\";\necho \"Copiados (config crítica): $copied\\n\";\necho \"Skipped (per-blog tracking): $skipped_count\\n\";\necho \"\\n\";\n\n// Validar que options críticas agora existem\n$check = [\"cmplz_purposes_pt\", \"cmplz_serviceTypes_pt\", \"complianz_active_policy_id\",\n          \"cmplz_privacy-statement_custom_page\", \"cmplz_cookie-statement_custom_page\",\n          \"cmplz_disclaimer_custom_page\", \"cmplz_publish_date\"];\nforeach ($check as $k) {\n    $v = get_option($k);\n    $type = is_array($v) ? \"array(\" . count($v) . \")\" : (is_scalar($v) ? substr((string)$v, 0, 40) : \"complex\");\n    echo \"  $k: \" . ($v === false ? \"MISSING\" : $type) . \"\\n\";\n}\n' 2>&1 | grep -v \"Cores\\|BIT BPO\\|│\\|╭\\|╰\\|├\\|Deprecated\" | tail -15\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== Flush cache + esperar regen ===\"\n$DEV_WP cache-flush 2>&1 | tail -2\n\nsleep 3\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== Validar HTML servido em blog 2 agora tem cmplz banner ===\"\necho -n \"/cultura/ — ocorrências cmplz no HTML: \"\ncurl -sk \"https://cambrasmax.local:8484/cultura/?cb=$(date +%s)\" | grep -ciE \"cmplz-banner|cmplz-cookiebanner|cmplz-accept|cmplz-deny\"","description":"Copy missing options + flush + validate"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2319,"cache_read_input_tokens":901531,"output_tokens":1445,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":2319,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[{"input_tokens":1,"output_tokens":1445,"cache_read_input_tokens":901531,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2319,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":2319},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"diagnostics":null},"requestId":"req_011Cacz8mcrE12Sh1g6BuELv","type":"assistant","uuid":"8002b653-904c-4900-ae2a-e10f937a3fd4","timestamp":"2026-05-02T02:53:31.062Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/dcambria/scripts/server-tools/v2/