{"parentUuid":"f0d9e5fd-6c6e-4786-8534-a87be833ad09","isSidechain":false,"promptId":"c2a75e50-561a-47e3-8f42-d172e1fee53e","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01RipaJz39zevRyRKmdjJv2f","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"### Result\n{\"blog1\":{\"banner_visible\":true,\"banner_text\":\"Gerenciar consentimento\\nPara proporcionar uma melhor experiência, usamos tecnologias como cookies pa\",\"accept\":\"ACEITAR\",\"deny\":\"REJEITAR\",\"cmplz_scripts\":1,\"window_complianz\":true},\"blog2_cultura\":{\"banner_visible\":true,\"banner_text\":\"Gerenciar consentimento\\nPara proporcionar uma melhor experiência, usamos tecnologias como cookies pa\",\"accept\":\"ACEITAR\",\"deny\":\"REJEITAR\",\"cmplz_scripts\":1,\"window_complianz\":true},\"blog2_atlas\":{\"banner_visible\":true,\"banner_text\":\"Gerenciar consentimento\\nPara proporcionar uma melhor experiência, usamos tecnologias como cookies pa\",\"accept\":\"ACEITAR\",\"deny\":\"REJEITAR\",\"cmplz_scripts\":1,\"window_complianz\":true}}\n### Ran Playwright code\n```js\nawait (async (page) => {\n  const audit = async (url) => {\n    await page.context().clearCookies();\n    await page.goto(url + '?cb=' + Date.now(), { waitUntil: 'networkidle', timeout: 30000 });\n    await page.waitForTimeout(3500);\n    return await page.evaluate(() => {\n      const banner = document.querySelector('.cmplz-cookiebanner, #cmplz-cookiebanner-container, [class*=\"cmplz-banner\"]');\n      return {\n        banner_visible: banner ? getComputedStyle(banner).display !== 'none' : false,\n        banner_text: banner?.innerText?.slice(0, 100) || null,\n        accept: document.querySelector('.cmplz-accept, [data-cmplz-action=\"accept\"]')?.innerText?.trim() || null,\n        deny: document.querySelector('.cmplz-deny, [data-cmplz-action=\"deny\"]')?.innerText?.trim() || null,\n        cmplz_scripts: Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('script[src]')).filter(s => /cmplz|complianz/i.test(s.src)).length,\n        window_complianz: typeof window.complianz !== 'undefined',\n      };\n    });\n  };\n  return {\n    blog1: await audit('https://concertacao.bureau-it.com/'),\n    blog2_cultura: await audit('https://concertacao.bureau-it.com/cultura/'),\n    blog2_atlas: await audit('https://concertacao.bureau-it.com/cultura/atlas-cultural-das-amazonias/'),\n  };\n})(page);\n```\n### Page\n- Page URL: https://concertacao.bureau-it.com/cultura/atlas-cultural-das-amazonias/?cb=1777690561152\n- Page Title: Atlas Cultural das Amazônias – Uma Concertação pela Amazonia: Cultura\n- Console: 0 errors, 4 warnings\n### Events\n- New console entries: ../tmp/playwright-output/console-2026-05-02T02-55-47-034Z.log#L1-L4\n- [LOG] JQMIGRATE: Migrate is installed with logging...wp-includes/js/jquery/jquery-migrate.js?ver=3.4.1:103\n- [LOG] opt-in @ https://concertacao.bureau-it.com/w...gdpr/cookiebanner/js/complianz.js?ver=1774279960:1102\n- [WARNING] JQMIGRATE: jQuery.type is deprecated @ h...wp-includes/js/jquery/jquery-migrate.js?ver=3.4.1:135\n- [WARNING] The resource https://concertacao.bureau-...https://concertacao.bureau-it.com/?cb=1777690547047:0\n- [LOG] JQMIGRATE: Migrate is installed with logging...wp-includes/js/jquery/jquery-migrate.js?ver=3.4.1:103\n- [LOG] opt-in @ https://concertacao.bureau-it.com/c...gdpr/cookiebanner/js/complianz.js?ver=1774279960:1102\n- [LOG] Fallback default css file used. Please re-sa...gdpr/cookiebanner/js/complianz.js?ver=1774279960:1177\n- [WARNING] The resource https://concertacao.bureau-...concertacao.bureau-it.com/cultura/?cb=1777690555870:0\n- [LOG] JQMIGRATE: Migrate is installed with logging...wp-includes/js/jquery/jquery-migrate.js?ver=3.4.1:103\n- [LOG] opt-in @ https://concertacao.bureau-it.com/c...gdpr/cookiebanner/js/complianz.js?ver=1774279960:1102\n- [LOG] Fallback default css file used. Please re-sa...gdpr/cookiebanner/js/complianz.js?ver=1774279960:1177\n- [WARNING] JQMIGRATE: jQuery.fn.click() event short...wp-includes/j