r-dev/common/scripts/cmplz-migrate-dev-to-prod.sh --site=<site-name> [--dry-run|--apply]\n\nARGS:\n  --site=<name>   Site no docker-dev (ex: concertacao). Obrigatorio.\n  --dry-run       Mostra o que seria copiado, nao escreve em prod (default)\n  --apply         Aplica as mudancas em prod\n  --help, -h      Exibe este help\n\nEXEMPLO:\n  /Users/dcambria/scripts/server-tools/v2/docker-dev/common/scripts/cmplz-migrate-dev-to-prod.sh --site=concertacao --dry-run\n  /Users/dcambria/scripts/server-tools/v2/docker-dev/common/scripts/cmplz-migrate-dev-to-prod.sh --site=concertacao --apply\n\nREQUISITOS:\n  - SSH alias <fqdn>-prod-sa configurado em ~/.ssh/config\n  - docker-dev rodando localmente (container do site UP)\n  - jq instalado (brew install jq)","is_error":false}]},"uuid":"d6101fb1-8eb9-491d-b639-cb98a354a6c5","timestamp":"2026-05-02T03:16:14.801Z","toolUseResult":{"stdout":"-rwxr-xr-x@ 1 dcambria  staff  15660  2 mai 00:16 /Users/dcambria/scripts/server-tools/v2/docker-dev/common/scripts/cmplz-migrate-dev-to-prod.sh\n\n=== Validar shellcheck ===\n\nIn /Users/dcambria/scripts/server-tools/v2/docker-dev/common/scripts/cmplz-migrate-dev-to-prod.sh line 173:\n    ssh \"$PROD_SSH_ALIAS\" \"sudo -u www-data wp --path=${PROD_WP_ROOT} --url=${blog_url} $*\" 2>/dev/null \\\n                                                      ^-------------^ SC2029 (info): Note that, unescaped, this expands on the client side.\n\n\nIn /Users/dcambria/scripts/server-tools/v2/docker-dev/common/scripts/cmplz-migrate-dev-to-prod.sh line 178:\nlist_dev_options() {\n^-- SC2329 (info): This function is never invoked. Check usage (or ignored if invoked indirectly).\n\n\nIn /Users/dcambria/scripts/server-tools/v2/docker-dev/common/scripts/cmplz-migrate-dev-to-prod.sh line 227:\nBACKUP_FILE=\"${WORK_DIR}/cmplz_prod_backup_${TS}.json\"\n^---------^ SC2034 (warning): BACKUP_FILE appears unused. Verify use (or export if used externally).\n\n\nIn /Users/dcambria/scripts/server-tools/v2/docker-dev/com