veForm":"Migrando para serving via CloudFront-OAC","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"36","subject":"Ciclo 3 ajustado: apply apenas green (canary, sem swap behavior principal)","description":"Publish CF Function + criar policies/origins + behavior canary específico para X-Test-Green. Blue intocado.","activeForm":"Aplicando CF-OAC apenas na green via canary path","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"37","subject":"B+C: canary multisite + validação E2E paridade visual","description":"Adicionar 2º behavior cobrindo /*/wp-content/uploads/_oac-canary/* + Playwright em 20 endpoints do A4","activeForm":"Adicionando canary multisite + validando E2E paridade visual","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"38","subject":"Ciclo 4: cutover real CF-OAC zero downtime","description":"Sync green→assets + swap behavior wp-content/uploads/* ALB→S3-uploads-prod + validate + ativar S3-Uploads no blue","activeForm":"Executando cutover real CF-OAC zero downtime","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"39","subject":"Re-import DB dev→green para corrigir WPML Atlas EN","description":"Export fresh dev DB → S3 green/sql → script 09 import → cleanup + flush. Setting WPML do dev tem display-as-translated correto.","activeForm":"Re-importando DB dev→green para corrigir Atlas EN","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"40","subject":"Documentar fix: Origin Request Policy default → Managed-AllViewer","description":"DefaultCacheBehavior OriginRequestPolicy mudada de WP-Dynamic-ForwardHostQS para Managed-AllViewer pra X-Test-Green chegar ao ALB","activeForm":"Documentando fix Origin Request Policy","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"41","subject":"Testar PDFs/jet_download em green","description":"Validar que PDFs e downloads via JetEngine funcionam na green com X-Test-Green","activeForm":"Testando PDFs/jet_download em green","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"42","subject":"Testar filtros da espiral em green","description":"Validar que cliques na espiral ativam filtros JetEngine em /conhecimento/espiral-de-conhecimento/","activeForm":"Testando filtros da espiral em green","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"43","subject":"Export DB dev + upload S3 dev/sql","description":"Rodar std export-db no dev (gera dump e sobe para s3://concertacao-backups/concertacao/dev/sql/)","activeForm":"Exportando DB do dev","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"44","subject":"Export wp-content dev + upload S3","description":"Rodar std export-wpcontent --include-uploads (sync incremental de mu-plugins, themes, plugins, uploads)","activeForm":"Exportando wp-content do dev","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"45","subject":"Copiar dev→green no S3","description":"aws s3 cp dos arquivos de dev/sql e dev/wp para green/sql e green/wp","activeForm":"Copiando arquivos dev→green no S3","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"46","subject":"Import DB na green via 09-importdatabase.sh","description":"SSH green-sa rodar 09-importdatabase.sh (drop+recreate DB, search-replace, ATE WPML cleanup, FQDN swap)","activeForm":"Importando DB na green","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"47","subject":"Import wp-content na green","description":"SSH green-sa rodar 10-importwpcontent.sh (themes/plugins/mu-plugins) + sync de uploads se necessario","activeForm":"Importando wp-content na green","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"48","subject":"Validar green pos-sync (smoke + jet_download + espiral)","description":"curl + comparacoes blue/green: home, atlas, jet_download, filtros JSF, salts (devem estar iguais ao blue)","activeForm":"Validando green pos-sync","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"49","subject":"Comparar dev vs green: páginas do menu","description":"Comparar visualmente/por content cada página: home, atlas, espiral, demais. Reportar diferenças e propor fix.","activeForm":"Comparando dev vs green pagina por pagina","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"50","subject":"Limpar S3 green de Elementor CSS vazado","description":"aws s3 rm dos post-XX.css em green/uploads/elementor/ e green/uploads/sites/2/elementor/ para garantir comportamento determinístico","activeForm":"Limpando S3 green de Elementor CSS vazado","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"51","subject":"Mu-plugin v2.0.0 com pre-warmup do static cache","description":"Reescrever bit-elementor-local-cache.php para pre-aquecer Base::$wp_uploads_dir com path local antes do S3-Uploads","activeForm":"Reescrevendo bit-elementor-local-cache v2.0.0","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"52","subject":"Deploy mu-plugin v2 na green + flush + regenerar","description":"Rsync mu-plugin novo para green, apagar elementor-cache antigo, wp elementor flush_css, validar URLs no HTML","activeForm":"Deployando mu-plugin v2 na green","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"53","subject":"CF behaviors */elementor/css/* → ALB (defesa em profundidade)","description":"Adicionar 4 behaviors CloudFront para capturar URLs legadas de elementor CSS em filesystem path → ALB","activeForm":"Adicionando CF behaviors elementor/css → ALB","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]},{"id":"54","subject":"Fix CF cache pollution + keepalive","description":"Auditoria 10 agentes — aplicar 3 fixes CF + Playwright + invalidate","activeForm":"Aplicando fixes CF","status":"completed","blocks":[],"blockedBy":[]}],"itemCount":32},"type":"attachment","uuid":"0c23f5d8-1666-4f23-8190-f8efc4160773","timestamp":"2026-05-02T03:41:25.415Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/dcambria/scripts/server-tools/v2/docker-dev/sites/concertacao","sessionId":"55811d4e-34d6-42df-9582-284664a6a576","version":"2.1.126","gitBranch":"main","slug":"prepare-o-deploy-do-snappy-taco"}
{"parentUuid":"0c23f5d8-1666-4f23-8190-f8efc4160773","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-7","id":"msg_018F8BUkQtW2cHbNvtnSV7Ee","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**Pendência 2 — fix encontrado:** `cmplz_update_all_banners()` é a função pra regenerar CSS files. Em prod blog 2 não existem CSS files em `/uploads/sites/2/complianz/`. Vou rodar essa função:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2254,"cache_read_input_tokens":963876,"output_tokens":1125,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":2254,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[{"input_tokens":1,"output_tokens":1125,"cache_read_input_tokens":963876,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2254,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":2254},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"diagnostics":null},"requestId":"req_011Cad3pMv3gpBfQWmgHVguV","type":"assistant","uuid":"1531620b-fb4d-4448-928e-b3882f382f05","timestamp":"2026-05-02T03:41:32.757Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/dcambria/scripts/server-tools/v2/docker-dev/sites/concertacao","sessionId":"55811d4e-34d6-42df-9582-284664a6a576","version":"2.1.126","gitBranch":"main","slug":"prepare-o-deploy-do-snappy-taco"}
{"parentUuid":"1531620b-fb4d-4448-928e-b3882f382f05","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-7","id":"msg_018F8BUkQtW2cHbNvtnSV7Ee","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_018ZjmAcoCFsZpwqe484kQce","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"echo \"=== Pendência 2: regenerar CSS dos banners em PROD ===\"\n\n# Criar dir se não existe + chown\nssh -n concertacaoamazonia.com.br-prod-sa \"\nsudo mkdir -p /var/www/concertacaoamazonia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/complianz/css\nsudo chown -R www-data:www-data /var/www/concertacaoamazonia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/complianz\nls -la /var/www/concertacaoamazonia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/complianz/\n\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== Chamar cmplz_update_all_banners() em ambos blogs ===\"\nssh -n concertacaoamazonia.com.br-prod-sa \"\necho '--- Blog 1 ---'\nsudo -u www-data wp --path=/var/www/concertacaoamazonia.com.br --url=https://concertacaoamazonia.com.br/ eval '\nif (function_exists(\\\"cmplz_update_all_banners\\\")) {\n    cmplz_update_all_banners();\n    echo \\\"cmplz_update_all_banners() called\\\\n\\\";\n}\nif (function_exists(\\\"cmplz_maybe_update_css\\\")) {\n    cmplz_maybe_update_css();\n    echo \\\"cmplz_maybe_update_css() called\\\\n\\\";\n}\n' 2>&1 | grep -v Deprecated | tail -3\n\necho '--- Blog 2 ---'\nsudo -u www-data wp --path=/var/www/concertacaoamazonia.com.br --url=https://concertacaoamazonia.com.br/cultura/ eval '\nif (function_exists(\\\"cmplz_update_all_banners\\\")) {\n    cmplz_update_all_banners();\n    echo \\\"cmplz_update_all_banners() called\\\\n\\\";\n}\nif (function_exists(\\\"cmplz_maybe_update_css\\\")) {\n    cmplz_maybe_update_css();\n    echo \\\"cmplz_maybe_update_css() called\\\\n\\\";\n}\n' 2>&1 | grep -v Deprecated | tail -3\n\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"=== CSS files agora? ===\"\necho \"--- blog 1 ---\"\nssh -n concertacaoamazonia.com.br-prod-sa \"sudo ls -la /var/www/concertacaoamazonia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/complianz/css/ 2>/dev/null\"\necho \"--- blog 2 ---\"\nssh -n concertacaoamazonia.com.br-prod-sa \"sudo ls -la /var/www/concertacaoamazonia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/complianz/css/ 2>/dev/null\"","description":"Regenerate banner CSS files"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2254,"cache_read_input_tokens":963876,"output_tokens":1125,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":2254,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[{"input_tokens":1,"output_tokens":1125,"cache_read_input_tokens":963876,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2254,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":2254},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"diagnostics":null},"requestId":"req_011Cad3pMv3gpBfQWmgHVguV","type":"assistant","uuid":"2b62fd65-dcd9-49cd-bf15-ae7c8f9449fd","timestamp":"2026-05-02T03:41:41.687Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/dcambria/scripts/server-tools/v2/docker-dev/sites/concertacao","sessionId":"55811d4e-34d6-42df-9582-284664a6a576","version":"2.1.126","gitBranch":"main","slug":"prepare-o-deploy-do-snappy-taco"}
{"parentUuid":"2b62fd65-dcd9-49cd-bf15-ae7c8f9449fd","isSidechain":false,"promptId":"358237b1-8c88-49db-af9f-ac8efe90fb13","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_018ZjmAcoCFsZpwqe484kQce","type":"tool_result","content":"=== Pendência 2: regenerar CSS dos banners em PROD ===\ntotal 12\ndrwxr-xr-x 3 www-data www-data 4096 mai  2 00:41 .\ndrwxr-xr-x 5 www-data www-data 4096 abr 29 19:59 ..\ndrwxr-xr-x 2 www-data www-data 4096 mai  2 00:41 css\n\n=== Chamar cmplz_update_all_banners() em ambos blogs ===\n--- Blog 1 ---\ncmplz_update_all_banners() called\ncmplz_maybe_update_css() called\n--- Blog 2 ---\ncmplz_update_all_banners() called\ncmplz_maybe_update_css() called\n\n=== CSS files agora? ===\n--- blog 1 ---\ntotal 40\ndrwxr-xr-x 2 www-data www-data  4096 mar 23 12:33 .\ndrwxr-xr-x 3 www-data www-data  4096 abr 28 20:24 ..\n-rw-r--r-- 1 www-data www-data 15925 mai  2 00:32 banner-1-optin.css\n-rw-r--r-- 1 www-data www-data 16034 mar 23 12:33 banner-1-optout.css\n--- blog 2 ---\ntotal 8\ndrwxr-xr-x 2 www-data www-data 4096 mai  2 00:41 .\ndrwxr-xr-x 3 www-data www-data 4096 mai  2 00:41 ..","is_error":false}]},"uuid":"26152552-12fd-4678-a405-af37a8108c92","timestamp":"2026-05-02T03:41:56.634Z","toolUseResult":{"stdout":"=== Pendência 2: regenerar CSS dos banners em PROD ===\ntotal 12\ndrwxr-xr-x 3 www-data www-data 4096 mai  2 00:41 .\ndrwxr-xr-x 5 www-data www-data 4096 abr 29 19:59 ..\ndrwxr-xr-x 2 www-data www-data 4096 mai  2 00:41 css\n\n=== Chamar cmplz_update_all_banners() em ambos blogs ===\n--- Blog 1 ---\ncmplz_update_all_banners() called\ncmplz_maybe_update_css() called\n--- Blog 2 ---\ncmplz_update_all_banners() called\ncmplz_maybe_update_css() called\n\n=== CSS files agora? ===\n--- blog 1 ---\ntotal 40\ndrwxr-xr-x 2 www-data www-data  4096 mar 23 12:33 .\ndrwxr-xr-x 3 www-data www-data  4096 abr 28 20:24 ..\n-rw-r--r-- 1 www-data www-data 15925 mai  2 00:32 banner-1-optin.css\n-rw-r--r-- 1 www-data www-data 16034 mar 23 12