{"parentUuid":"0ed73ae5-b220-417a-8804-6d865370a5bc","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-7","id":"msg_018gCEm3yddN1e2uay7uAYUQ","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Resultados do smoke:\n\n**3 problemas detectados:**\n\n1. **Blog 2 (`/cultura/`)** — `banner_visible: false` + erro 404 no console: `/uploads/sites/2/complianz/css/banner-1-optin.css?v=6` (CloudFront ainda servindo cache antigo)\n2. **Blog 1 EN (`/en/`)** — banner_visible=true mas com texto **\"ACEITAR\"/\"REJEITAR\"** (PT, não EN) — falta tradução WPML\n3. **HTML lang em `/cultura/`** está `pt-br` mas deveria refletir o subsite\n\nO Blog 2 erro 404 é cache CF — o arquivo existe no servidor (16025 bytes), só não propagou. Vou checar status da invalidação:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":6,"cache_creation_input_tokens":5276,"cache_read_input_tokens":110686,"output_tokens":534,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":5276,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[{"input_tokens":6,"output_tokens":534,"cache_read_input_tokens":110686,"cache_creation_input_tokens":5276,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":5276},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"diagnostics":null},"requestId":"req_011Cad4Uki4MNDYbMbJGWFCi","type":"assistant","uuid":"37dda25f-b23e-4172-b8f1-eb5d946c0eb7","timestamp":"2026-05-02T03:50:14.043Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/dcambria/scripts/server-tools/v2/docker-dev/sites/concertacao","sessionId":"55811d4e-34d6-42df-9582-284664a6a576","version":"2.1.126","gitBranch":"main","slug":"prepare-o-deploy-do-snappy-taco"}
